富士X100F（X100系列第四代）发布于2017年1月19日<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.fujifilm.com/news/n170119_02.html|title=Premium Compact Digital Camera "FUJIFILM X100F" — X Series' most powerful new addition featuring the latest 24.3 megapixel sensor and processor|newspaper=Fujifilm Global|language=en-US|access-date=2017-01-19|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126045929/https://www.fujifilm.com/news/n170119_02.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，这是[[富士X100T|富士X100T]]的继任产品。它对上一代进行了许多改进和增强，其中许多功能是从[[富士X-Pro2|富士X-Pro2]]引入的，而这部分功能在X-Pro2之前从没有发布过。 X100F于2017年2月23日对外发售。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.fujirumors.com/fujifilm-x100f-x-t20-x-t2-graphite-xf50mm-final-release-date-press-release/|title=Fujifilm X100F, X-T20, X-T2 Graphite & XF50mm Final Release Date - PRESS RELEASE - Fuji Rumors|date=2017-01-31|newspaper=Fuji Rumors|language=en-US|access-date=2017-01-31|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213110343/https://www.fujirumors.com/fujifilm-x100f-x-t20-x-t2-graphite-xf50mm-final-release-date-press-release/|dead-url=no}}</ref>下一代继任产品富士X100V于2020年2月4日发布。

== 与上一代X100T的不同 ==

* 一个第三代的2430万像素的 [[Fujifilm_X-Trans_sensor|X-Trans CMOS III]] 传感器
* X-Processor Pro 图像处理器
* 带有操纵杆自动对焦控制的新按钮布局（类似于[[X-Pro2|X-Pro2]]和[[富士X-T2|X-T2]]），选择自动对焦点更加容易<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2017/1/19/14324456/fujifilm-x100f-x-t20-cameras-hands-on-first-look|title=Hands on with Fujifilm’s new X100F and X-T20|last=Seifert|first=Dan|newspaper=The Verge|access-date=2017-01-19|archive-date=2020-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201212120312/https://www.theverge.com/circuitbreaker/2017/1/19/14324456/fujifilm-x100f-x-t20-cameras-hands-on-first-look|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 内置ISO拨盘
* 在相机正面添加了指令拨盘
* 曝光补偿拨盘上的C模式，最多可实现5档曝光补偿
* 更换了更大的电池（NP-W126S，与X-T2相同）
* 改进的91点自动对焦系统
* 更高的感光度（ISO 200–12800，可扩展至ISO 100–51200）
* 取景器可实现6倍放大
* Acros底片模拟（成像色彩接近富士 Acros 100胶卷）
* 电子取景器刷新率达到每秒60帧<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fujifilm X100F - Feature 4 Performance|url=http://www.fujifilm.com/products/digital_cameras/x/fujifilm_x100f/features/page_04.html|date=|last=|first=|publisher=|language=en-US|website=Fujifilm Global|access-date=2017-01-19|archive-date=2019-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190318063104/http://www.fujifilm.com/products/digital_cameras/x/fujifilm_x100f/features/page_04.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 额外的连续拍摄模式速度（3、4、5和8 fps）以及更大的缓冲区
* 新型LED自动对焦辅助灯
* 模拟等效35mm 50毫米和70毫米视角的数字变焦功能（仅JPG）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fujifilm X100F|url=http://www.fujifilm.com/products/digital_cameras/x/fujifilm_x100f/specifications/|date=|last=|first=|publisher=|language=en-US|website=Fujifilm Global|access-date=2017-01-19|archive-date=2019-12-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191212111734/https://www.fujifilm.com/products/digital_cameras/x/fujifilm_x100f/specifications/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 反响 ==
X100F非常受用户欢迎，主要是因为其改进的传感器和自动对焦功能。 Digital Photography Review给它的评分为83％，并获得了金奖，称其为“真正的摄影师的相机”（a true photographers' camera）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Fujifilm X100F|url=https://m.dpreview.com/products/fujifilm/compacts/fujifilm_x100f|website=Digital Photography Review|access-date=2020-11-29|archive-date=2019-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191228091735/https://m.dpreview.com/products/fujifilm/compacts/fujifilm_x100f|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 

在2017年技术影像新闻协会奖上，X100F赢得了最佳专业紧凑型相机奖<ref>{{Cite web|title=TIPA - TECHNICAL IMAGE PRESS ASSOCIATION - This year's awards|url=http://www.tipa.com/english/XXVII_tipa_awards_2017.html|language=it|website=www.tipa.com|access-date=2017-10-24|archive-date=2020-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201209002022/https://www.tipa.com/english/XXVII_tipa_awards_2017.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

